CustomField.description: Income of Participant Name 4 which also rolls up to the Combined Gross Annual Income
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Gross annual income is the sum of your ‘assessable’ (or taxable) income and your ‘exempt’ income (as defined on the ATO website). If you have a salary sacrifice arrangement, your Gross Annual Income needs to be adjusted to reflect the arrangement.
